Posts.Content: I am 56 yrs old and was diagnosed with stage IV met breast cancer I just started chemo as my hormone therapy is not working anymore.  My cancer is active now first chemo treatment was terribly rough - next treatment is April 19 any suggestions out there for side effects or has anyone been using protecel with paw paw with any good results.  I have a healthy diet but have lost 40 lbs over the last year I was overwieght so not any real concern there unless I continue to lose wieght.  Any one in my situation?  Could use a friend that may be in the same situation!
Posts.Title: Do I have anything in common with you ?
